snippet.title: Dune Legacy 0.96.3
snippet.description: Dune Legacy is an open source remake of Dune II. New features include multiple unit selection/control, high resolution support, multiplayer gaming and an improved GUI. For further information see http://dunelegacy.sourceforge.net
